data.title: WordPress › Error
data.text:
User booksby already has more than 'max_user_connections' active connections

Error establishing a database connection

This either means that the username and password information in your wp-config.php file is incorrect or that contact with the database server at booksbywomenorg.netfirmsmysql.com could not be established. This could mean your host’s database server is down.

Are you sure you have the correct username and password?

Are you sure you have typed the correct hostname?

Are you sure the database server is running?
